=== un-narrowed object arithmetic not allowed
def f(x: object) -> int:
    return x + 1
---
error: object
---

=== un-narrowed object method call not allowed
def f(x: object) -> str:
    return x.upper()
---
error: object
---

=== un-narrowed object subscript not allowed
def f(x: object) -> int:
    return x[0]
---
error: object
---

=== un-narrowed object comparison allowed
def f(x: object, y: object) -> bool:
    return x == y
---
ok
---

=== repr on object allowed
def f(x: object) -> str:
    return repr(x)
---
ok
